Files in this component and their provenance:

  src/crc.c, src/crc.h
      Vendored verbatim from dump1090 crc.{c,h}. Mode-S 24-bit CRC and
      (unused here) error-correction syndrome tables. Original include of
      "dump1090.h" replaced with self-contained definitions; otherwise
      unchanged.

  src/cpr.c, src/cpr.h
      Vendored verbatim from dump1090 cpr.{c,h}. Compact Position Reporting
      (CPR) airborne/surface/relative decode + the NL latitude-zone table.

  src/ais_charset.c, src/ais_charset.h
      Vendored verbatim from dump1090. 6-bit AIS character set used for
      callsign (TC 1-4) decode.

  src/mode_s_decode.c, src/mode_s_decode.h
      Ported (not verbatim) from dump1090 mode_s.c. The getbit/getbits
      helpers are copied verbatim from mode_s.h. The Extended-Squitter
      decoders (ident TC1-4, surface TC5-8, airborne position TC9-22,
      velocity TC19, operational status TC31) and the DF routing in
      decodeModesMessage are reimplemented onto a slim ms_msg_t struct,
      keeping the original field-extraction math. The DSP front-end,
      message scoring, brute-force error correction, comm-b, MRAR, nav,
      and the SDR/threading layers are intentionally not ported — the
      Pong delivers already-demodulated, FEC-corrected frames.

  src/cpr_store.c
      Stratux-esp32 original. Per-ICAO even/odd CPR staging with expiry,
      driving the vendored cpr.c global/relative decoders.
